title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Feb 02 WE [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 02 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


Wednesday's guest is Peter Wallison, AEI's fellow in financial policy studies and member of the Financial Crisis Inquiry Commission (FCIC), on how his government task force somehow neglected to detect any public-sector culpability for the financial crisis.
